deck: George Amaru is a freelance comic artist/illustrator and graphic designer, working in southwest New Hampshire. He is best known for his creator-owned title, Legacy of the Falcon, his work with GrayHaven Comics and as artist on the weekly webcomic, "New Comic Day." George works in both traditional media, such as pencil, ink, charcoal and pastels as well as digital media.
